title: Glass Jar
description: A clear glass jar with a metal clip lid. The jar has a rounded body and a wide mouth, making it suitable for storing various items.

title: Map and Compass
description: An image featuring a compass placed on top of a folded map. The map displays various roads and routes, with a focus on the geographical layout. The compass is circular with a black face and a needle indicating direction.

title: Smartphone
description: An image of a black smartphone with a blue screen. The phone has a simple design with a home button and a few icons at the bottom.

title: Digital Camera
description: A black digital single-lens reflex (DSLR) camera with a prominent lens. The camera features a textured grip and various buttons on the body, indicating it is designed for professional photography.

title: Binoculars
description: A pair of black binoculars with textured grips and purple-tinted lenses, positioned on a white background.

title: Geologist's Tools
description: An image featuring a geological hammer with a blue handle and a rock beside it. The hammer has a flat side for breaking rocks and a pointed side for prying.

title: Entomological Notebook
description: An open spiral-bound notebook displaying handwritten notes on the left page and illustrations of insects on the right page. The left page contains dense, cursive writing, while the right page features detailed drawings of two different insects, possibly beetles, along with labels and descriptions.
